  "texts": [
    "Hence, even having individualised the estimation of the expected claims cost on a very granular level does not jeopardise the diversification effect of randomness.",
    "Actuaries have a unique role in their areas and have critical responsibilities for the management and understanding of the risk both the company is exposed to and that it continues as a sustainable entity.",
    "Traditional insurance and risk pooling allow for the transfer of risk from individuals to insurers to reinsurers, protecting the individual and the public in times of need.",
    "On average, everybody benefits.",
    "Through AI and data science with large datasets, individual risk assessment might become possible which could result in a trade-off between pricing on an individual basis and maximising commercial interests."
